<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.1.2">
<l>uṟavu cuṟṟameṉ ṟoṉṟi lāvoru vaṉu kantavar</l>
<l>tammai maṇmicaip</l>
<l>piṟavi yēkeṭup pāṉa tukaṇṭeṉ neñcamaṉpāy</l>
<l>kuṟavar mātarka ḷōṭu vaṇṭuku ṟiñci maruḷicai</l>
<l>pāṭum vēṅkaṭat</l>
<l>taṟava nāyakaṟ kiṉṟa ṭimaittoḻil pūṇṭāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O My companion heart, having seen that he destroys rebirth on this earth</l>
<l>For those who rejoice in [him], the one without any attachments or relations,</l>
<l>Today you assumed the duty of service to our virtuous one,</l>
<l rend="indent">the master of Vēṅkaṭam,</l>
<l>Where bees sing kuṟiñci tunes of wonderment along with hill maidens.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
